{"word":"G1645 - ἐλαφρός - elaphrós - el-af-ros' - Light","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐλαφρός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">elaphrós</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">el-af-ros'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Light</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"இலகுவான, இலேசான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"light in weight, quick, agile"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Probably akin to <a href=\"#/G1643 - ἐλαύνω - elaúnō - el-ow'-no/1643\">G1643</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G1640 - ἐλάσσων - elássōn - el-as'-sone/1640\">G1640</a>; <i>light</i>, that is, <i>easy:</i> - light.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}